com.jess.arms.widget.boxing.model.config

类 BoxingConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jess.arms.widget.boxing.model.config.BoxingConfig
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class BoxingConfig
extends Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    The pick config.
    1.BoxingConfig.Mode is necessary.
    2.specify functions: camera, gif, paging.
    calling #needCamera() to displayThumbnail a camera icon.
    calling needGif() to displayThumbnail gif photos.
    calling needPaging(boolean) to create load medias page by page, by default is true.
    作者:
    ChenSL
